snippet.title: The Dark Pictures Anthology - Man of Medan: Launch Trailer | PS4, X1, PC
snippet.description:
Take a final look at #ManofMedan before you delve into the first terrifying game from #TheDarkPictures Anthology!

Don’t … Play… Alone! Out August 30th on PS4, Xbox One & PC Digital. Order your copy today: https://bandainam.co/manofmedan

#TheDarkPictures #BandaiNamco
